stickerText:
Soft Sandwich Bread Recipe
(No Dairy or Eggs)

contents.desc: Recipe:
1 cup warm water
2 Tbsp sugar
2 ¾ tsp yeast
Mix until dissolved, then let sit 10 minutes.
Sourdough, if desired
¼ cup olive oil
1 ½ tsp salt
3 cups flour
Knead 3-4 minutes.
Cover and let sit 1 ½ hours.
Knead for one minute. Oil a loaf pan and fold dough into loaf shape.
Let sit for 1 hour.
Bake at 350 for 30 minutes.
